{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GamepadHapticActuator.pulse()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadHapticActuator/pulse","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadHapticActuator\"><code>GamepadHapticActuator</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadHapticActuator/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadHapticActuator/playEffect\"><code>playEffect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>pulse()</code></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadHapticActuator\"><code>GamepadHapticActuator</code></a> インターフェイスの&nbsp;<strong><code>pulse()</code></strong>&nbsp;メソッドは、指定された期間、特定の強度でハードウェアパルスを作成します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>gamepadHapticActuatorInstance<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pulse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> duration<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">result</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"パラメータ","title":"パラメータ","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"value\"><em>value</em></dt>\n <dd>パルスの強度を表す double 。これはハードウェアの型によって異なりますが、通常は&nbsp;0.0 (強度なし) から 1.0 (完全な強度)&nbsp;の値を取ります。</dd>\n <dt id=\"duration\"><em>duration</em></dt>\n <dd>パルスの持続時間をミリ秒で表す double 。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: <code>pulse()</code>&nbsp;への繰り返しの呼び出しは、それらがまた進行中である場合、以前の呼び出しをオーバーライドします。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返り値","title":"返り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>パルスが正常に完了したときに&nbsp;<code>true</code>&nbsp;の値で解決される promise 。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>TBC</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ステータス</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/extensions.html#dom-gamepadhapticactuator-pulse\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad Extensions<br><small lang=\"ja\">pulse() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-ed\">編集者草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</ta